# Implementation Checklist

## Operationalizing Ethics in Your Pipeline

### Day One
- [ ] Implement explainability mechanisms
- [ ] Set up audit trail logging
- [ ] Define human oversight protocols

### Data Preparation
- [ ] Test on diverse Ghanaian data
- [ ] Validate representation across demographics
- [ ] Implement anonymization procedures
- [ ] Obtain explicit consent

### Development
- [ ] Follow privacy best practices
- [ ] Build fairness testing into CI/CD
- [ ] Create transparency documentation
- [ ] Establish safety validation gates

### Pre-Deployment
- [ ] Complete ALTAI checklist
- [ ] Run bias assessments
- [ ] Document model decisions
- [ ] Prepare compliance reports

### Post-Deployment
- [ ] Monitor for bias drift
- [ ] Maintain audit trails
- [ ] Regular fairness assessments
- [ ] User feedback mechanisms

## Compliance Framework
1. **Legal** - Meets regulatory requirements
2. **Robust** - Performs reliably
3. **Ethical** - Respects human values

## Tools to Use
- ALTAI Checklist for readiness
- Policy Observatory for regulation tracking
- Open-source fairness toolkits
- XAI platforms (Vertex AI, IBM AIX360)
